{"tid":1456713,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"緊急 個人對機場熄燈斷網既睇法","createTime":"2019-08-12T10:39:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-12T10:49:39.000Z","uid":36876,"like":4,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"bfc18922d17c7b00bfa568882f92082e239beeca","tid":1456713,"uid":36876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T10:39:17.000Z","msg":"由於連登充斥大量假消息<br />\n我先假設早前真係有熄燈同斷過網<br />\n呢個可能係警方測試系統  到清場時將利用以上手段作大規模震壓  到時記者斷線做唔到直播  係屋企既人根本唔會知道發生咩事 希望各位手足小心 去留自己衡量"},{"pid":"e666d0312fed55e18c73b7f2fc6b02896bf0aebc","tid":1456713,"uid":277659,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T10:40:08.000Z","msg":"冇人熄燈呀屌你"},{"pid":"07fc50d2d2f7160074ab580bb81409c4005ec681","tid":1456713,"uid":8014,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T10:40:15.000Z","msg":"假撚到 根本人多所以先上唔到"},{"pid":"7f542e94bab32655a73a7c1595f41f42bb31eb21","tid":1456713,"uid":28307,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T10:43:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>由於連登充斥大量假消息<br />\n我先假設早前真係有熄燈同斷過網<br />\n呢個可能係警方測試系統  到清場時將利用以上手段作大規模震壓  到時記者斷線做唔到直播  係屋企既人根本唔會知道發生咩事 希望各位手足小心 去留自己衡量</blockquote><br />\n既可以製造白色恐怖<br />\n等和理非唔敢再去機場宣傳<br />\n<br />\n同樣地<br />\n睇佢地行動咁快 咁敏感<br />\n即係表示 香港機場係至關重要<br />\n<br />\n我地 以後更加要 經常性地去機場和平宣傳<br />\n等佢地自斷手腳 or 我地 斷佢經濟命脈"},{"pid":"ca5afe7e66b6687d65fb64b2166708bc8a74baac","tid":1456713,"uid":36876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T10:44:07.000Z","msg":"好似話航班恢復 大家唔洗理我呢個post了"},{"pid":"3f6e2d8a5b7316c6819a3127b81058fb5478e0ab","tid":1456713,"uid":28307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e666d0312fed55e18c73b7f2fc6b02896bf0aebc","tid":1456713,"uid":277659,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T10:40:08.000Z","msg":"冇人熄燈呀屌你"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T10:45:09.000Z","msg":"燈冇熄<br />\n但signal呢樣有冇熄過<br />\n根本好難fact checked到<br />\n有都唔奇<br />\n始終封鎖消息係共狗慣用技倆"},{"pid":"f17a8f99ea8ff8814d96f44a8f1f5b178676248d","tid":1456713,"uid":271617,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T10:45:31.000Z","msg":"目前我人仍在機埸，明白大家對於近日的抗議有一定憂慮，但實在無需過分恐慌，一些假消息傳出去也是不必要的。<br />\n<br />\n一、<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">#香港機場沒有切斷任何網絡</span></span>，順粹是人群聚集後網絡收得很差而已，過去遊行人數多的時候也有同樣狀況。<br />\n<br />\n二、目前機場燈火通明，機場快綫及機場巴士仍正常運作，有推着行李的香港人仍然繼續前往機場，亦有示威者正在陸續離開，包括沿機場路步行至東涌。<br />\n<br />\n三、客運大樓的大部份商店已落閘，現場所見仍有過千名示威者於接機大堂。<br />\n<br />\n四、目前仍有班機等待抵港，包括夜晚8:30的班機，亦有班機等待飛離香港。<br />\n<br />\nBy：黃之峰 facebook 現場 18:17"},{"pid":"f98687f5861d9346a0fed822aa6da5d8f395a5eb","tid":1456713,"uid":245292,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T10:45:49.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">機場live，三個source</span></span></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/hongkongfp/videos/395742341081446/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fhongkongfp%2Fvideos%2F395742341081446%2F&d=nSJvRvahoV7vX7tkwZxFzkUPjIZJXyGGplxIPwZjN5A%3D&h=fb8e5e07\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/hongkongfp/videos/395742341081446/</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=YemfPQ2o7Sc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DYemfPQ2o7Sc&d=nSJvRvahoV7vX7tkwZxFzkUPjIZJXyGGplxIPwZjN5A%3D&h=fef7d648\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=YemfPQ2o7Sc</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=e4juPPrdZYM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3De4juPPrdZYM&d=nSJvRvahoV7vX7tkwZxFzkUPjIZJXyGGplxIPwZjN5A%3D&h=593a1852\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=e4juPPrdZYM</a>"},{"pid":"a41eaa261d23a3c99690e0be7f7d144df5de5527","tid":1456713,"uid":168250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T10:46:37.000Z","msg":"今日成個連登嘅熱門post冇人fact check 咩6點清場 政府cut交通同網絡 t1熄燈 全部都係流料 成班人俾人帶晒風向"